quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  9,112,"Ko tuuboo…ďe …ďeen, rewoo…ďe (Alla) …ďeen, yettoo…ďe (Mo) …ďeen, hooroo…ďe …ďeen, ru∆ī∆īoo…ďe …ďeen, sujjoo…ďe …ďeen, yamiroo…ďe ko mo∆ī∆īi …ďeen ka…óa ko boni, e reenotoo…ďe e keeri Alla …óiin.weltin gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen."
  9,113,"Haananaa Annabiijo on e …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe nde …ďe imsinantoo sirkoo…ďe …ďen, hay si …ďen laatike joomiraa…ďe …ďadondiral, …ďaawo nde fee√Īani …ďe won de ko…ďe yim…ďe Jahiimi."
  9,114,"Imsinanagol Ibraahiima ngol baaaba makko wonaano si wanaa fodoore nde o fodannnoo mo. Tuma nde …ďanngannoo mo won de on ko ga√Īo Alla, o da…óndino(hisnii) mo. Pellet, Ibraahiima ko heewu…óo yankinaare, mu√Ī√Īii…óo."
  9,115,"Alla siforaali majjinoowo yim…ďe …ďaawo nde o feewni …ďe, haa O …ďannginana …ďe ko …ďe kaani reentaade e mu'um. Pellet, Alla ko ganndu…óo kala huunde."
  9,116,"Pellet, Ko Alla woodani laamu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo wuurna, himo wara. Alanaa on gah Alla gi…óo, wanaa balloowo"
  9,117,"Wollahi Alla ja…ďanii Annabiijo on tuubuubuyee, e fer…ďe …ďeen e wallu…ďe weerni …ďen jokku…ďe e saa'a sa…ótu…óo, …ďaawo nde …ďer…óe wo…ó…ďe e ma…ď…ďe e…ď…ďunoo oo√Īaade. refti Alla ja…ďani …ďe tuubgol. Pellet, KaŇčko ko O jaafotooo…óo, jumotoo…óo …ďe."